    </div>

    <div class="upgrades-bar">
      <span class="upgrades-label">Optional Upgrades:</span>
      <span>📸 Professional Photographer <em>(groups 17+)</em></span>
      <span>🍾 VIP Bottle Service</span>
      <span>⏱ Extra Bus Hour</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CLUB FINDER -->
<section id="clubs" class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Interactive</div>
    <h2>What's Open <span class="neon-text">On Your Night?</span></h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Pick your date and see which Vegas nightclubs are typically available. Our team finalizes the exact venue — but this gives you a real picture of what to expect.</p>

    <div class="finder-wrap">
      <div class="finder-input">
        <label for="eventDate">Select Your Date</label>
        <input type="date" id="eventDate" />
        <p class="finder-hint">Choose a date to see club options for that night</p>
      </div>

      <div id="clubResults" class="finder-results hidden">
        <div class="finder-results-top">
          <div id="resultsDay" class="res-day"></div>
          <div id="resultsCount" class="res-count"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="clubGrid" class="clubs-grid"></div>
        <div id="blackoutNote" class="blackout hidden">
          ⚠️ <strong>Major artist events</strong> (Calvin Harris, John Summit, Martin Garrix, etc.) on busy nights may affect club availability.
          <a href="mailto:info@gxptours.com">Email us to confirm →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="finder-ctas">
          <a href="https://gxptours.rezdy.com" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">Book for This Date →</a>
          <a href="tel:+17024830463" class="btn-ghost">📞 Call to Confirm</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how-it-works" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">The Experience</div>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">We coordinate every detail so your group can focus on having the best night of their lives.</p>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <img src="https://gxptours.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/MXZ03137-1024x576.webp" alt="Book your date" loading="lazy" />
        <h3>Book Your Date</h3>
        <p>Choose your package, lock in your headcount (4–100+ people). Your group stays 100% private — no strangers ever mixed in.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <img src="https://gxptours.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Dutch-Bros-Bus-Party-074.webp" alt="We plan everything" loading="lazy" />
        <h3>We Handle Everything</h3>
        <p>GXP schedules the lounge, nightclub entry, timing, and your driver. Every detail is handled — you don't lift a finger.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <img src="https://gxptours.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/MXZ08018-Enhanced-NR-1024x576.webp" alt="Party bus" loading="lazy" />
        <h3>Your Bus Arrives</h3>
        <p>Private party bus picks up your group. Champagne flowing, your music on, Las Vegas Sign photo stop included.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <img src="https://gxptours.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/MMLB3366_websize.jpg" alt="VIP nightclub entry" loading="lazy" />
        <h3>VIP Nightclub Entry</h3>
        <p>Skip the line. Walk straight in. One of Vegas's best clubs — already arranged, already paid for.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FLEET -->
<section class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">The Fleet</div>
    <h2>Your Vehicle Scales With Your Group</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">We automatically match the right vehicle to your headcount. Every tier is luxury.</p>
    <div class="fleet-grid">
      <div class="fleet-card"><div class="ft">Tier 1</div><div class="fi">🚗</div><div class="fn">Stretch Sedan Limo</div><div class="fs">Small groups</div></div>
      <div class="fleet-card"><div class="ft">Tier 2</div><div class="fi">🚐</div><div class="fn">Sprinter Limo</div><div class="fs">Up to 8</div></div>
      <div class="fleet-card"><div class="ft">Tier 3</div><div class="fi">🚌</div><div class="fn">XL Sprinter Limo</div><div class="fs">Up to 12</div></div>
      <div class="fleet-card"><div class="ft">Tier 4</div><div class="fi">🛻</div><div class="fn">Stretch Hummer Limo</div><div class="fs">Up to 18</div></div>
      <div class="fleet-card fleet-hot"><div class="ft">Tier 5</div><div class="fi">🚌</div><div class="fn">Party Bus</div><div class="fs">Up to 25</div></div>
      <div class="fleet-card fleet-hot"><div class="ft">Tier 6</div><div class="fi">🚌</div><div class="fn">XL Party Bus</div><div class="fs">Up to 45</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- URGENCY -->
<section class="section urgency">
