      <div class="review">
        <div class="rv-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>"I've done Vegas many times. This is by far the best way to experience the nightlife. No stress, no hidden costs. GXP makes you feel like a celebrity."</p>
        <cite>— Jessica R.</cite>
