    </div>
    <div class="press-bar">
      <span class="press-label">As Featured In</span>
      <div class="press-names">
        <span>Daily Mail Online</span>
        <span>ITV UK / Channel 5</span>
        <span>Bold Journey Magazine</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INCLUSIONS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">All-Inclusive</div>
    <h2>Everything Included. <span class="neon-text">Zero Surprises.</span></h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Other companies charge separately for gratuity, beverages, and club entry. We include it all — what you see is what you pay.</p>
    <div class="inc-grid">
      <div class="inc"><div class="inc-i">🥂</div><h4>Champagne & Bar Setup</h4><p>Complimentary champagne from the moment you board. Mixers, ice, cups included.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="inc-i">🎵</div><h4>Your Playlist</h4><p>Bluetooth audio on the bus — play whatever gets your group hyped.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="inc-i">📸</div><h4>Las Vegas Sign Stop</h4><p>The iconic photo every Vegas visitor needs. We stop so your whole group gets the shot.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="inc-i">🚪</div><h4>VIP Nightclub Entry</h4><p>Skip the line entirely. Walk straight into one of Vegas's top clubs. Already arranged.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="inc-i">🍺</div><h4>BYOB Welcome</h4><p>Bring your own drinks too — BYOB always welcome on the bus.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="inc-i">💰</div><h4>Gratuity Included</h4><p>No awkward tipping at the end. Driver gratuity is built into the price.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Questions</div>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details><summary>What's the dress code?</summary><div>Dress to impress for the nightclub. No flip-flops, sports jerseys, workout clothes, baseball caps, or offensive imagery. Smart casual or club attire works. No dress code required to board the party bus.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Is our group kept private the whole time?</summary><div>100%. Your group is never paired with strangers. Private bus, private lounge time, private nightclub entry — the entire experience is exclusively yours.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can we bring our own drinks (BYOB)?</summary><div>Yes — the party bus is BYOB-friendly. We also provide complimentary champagne, mixers, cups, straws, napkins, and fresh ice. Responsible drinking is expected throughout.</div></details>
      <details><summary>What if someone is under 21?</summary><div>All participants must be 21+ with a valid ID, checked at three points during the experience. Exception: 21st birthday guests are welcome if the reservation starts at midnight or later.</div></details>
      <details><summary>How far in advance should we book?</summary><div>1–2 weeks for regular weekends. For major events (EDC, Memorial Day, 4th of July, NYE, large conferences) book 4–6 weeks ahead — those dates sell out fast.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can we choose our nightclub?</summary><div>You can express a preference and we'll do our best. Available clubs rotate by day based on schedules. Use the club finder above to see what's typically open on your date.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Where do you pick us up?</summary><div>Hotels, lounges, and event locations across Las Vegas, Henderson, Summerlin, Southwest, and North Las Vegas. Off-Strip and Airbnb pickups accommodated (may slightly adjust timing).</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can we split the payment?</summary><div>Yes — payment splits up to 3 ways. Contact us to arrange the best setup for larger groups.</div></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FINAL CTA -->
<section class="final-cta">
